# 视频解析代理地址配置
# 请填写你部署的代理服务地址
# 
# 支持的代理平台：
# - Cloudflare Workers: https://your-worker.yourname.workers.dev
# - Vercel Functions:   https://your-project.vercel.app
# - Render.com:        https://your-service.onrender.com
# - Railway.app:       https://your-service.railway.app
# - Fly.io:            https://your-service.fly.dev
#
# 注意：必须以 VITE_ 开头，Vite 才能读取
# VITE_PROXY_URL=https://your-proxy-url.workers.dev